bookContent1=The adult world is boring, and they are always complaining about us kids. \\nI I heard that there is a place called Sky Island, and the best children can become the gods of creation  there. \\n
bookContent2=Good morning, Sky Island. Now I'm standing here on the edge of the island and watching the sun rise, all the hardships from the journey were worth it. \\nYes, they are right. You are the Utopia for children, and the adventure wonderland that every warrior wants to conquer. \\n
bookContent3=Oh,such an annoying but fascinating Sky Island! It is really tough to survive here.\\nIt seems that I need to hand-down some skills for others.\\nHey, newbies, two important tips for you: \\n1, Click all the buttons and clickable pictures to explore this land better. \\n2, Changing the walking mode to sneaking mode, which will ensure that you will not fall while building. \\n
bookContent4=Hey, I think you've noticed that there are a lot of floating islands around. \\nThere are gifts left by the pioneer adventurers, and some of them are from me. \\nFind them! Expand your island with blocks. By the way, you can get blocks from your miner machine and mining area. \\n
bookContent5=Time flies so fast, I have been here for two years. I met many friends here. \\nSome of them are old castle fanatics, and took me to visit their castles and islands. \\nAnd some of them are fighting enthusiasts,  who took me to the mining area to fight with dragons. \\nThis is a world filled with all kinds of magnificent fantasies...\\nYeah, I fell in love with this place! I will stay. \\n
bookContent6=Good morning, today is a day worth looking forward to. \\nOld Jack taught me 2 skills yesterday, and I can finally try now. And do you wanna try with me? \\n1. Plowing on soil block or grass block with a hoe, and then you can plant different crop seeds on it. \\n2. Sprinkling bone powder on the soil, then it will grow a variety of flowers, which can be used to make dyes in the craft table.\\n
bookContent7=Hey, the world will change every two weeks. \\nI've witnessed how this impefect world to improve over time. \\nBelieve it, and give it time and patience, it will reward you with beauty and miracles. \\n
bookContent8=Good morning, my friends. \\nI haven't seen your island yet since we met . \\nIf there is a chance, would you like to show it in another world and let everyone see it? \\nI really want everyone to see it. Don't be shy. You have worked so hard, and it must be as perfect as it can be.\\n
