Item_Name560002=[Sky Block] Public Beta Testing Opening Announcement
Item_Name560003=[Sky Block] Fair Game Operation Statement
Item_Name570001=Event Time: December 31th 00:00 ~ February 1th 00:00\\n\\nActivity 1: Login to receive 7 days Christmas gifts\\nActivity Description: During the activity, players can login to the game to receive 7 days login rewards. On the 7th day, players will receive a Christmas tree that can be placed on the island.\\n\\nActivity 2: The Messenger of Christmas\\nActivity Description: There will comes the Christmas messenger and Christmas tree in the island lobby. All players can click the Christmas tree once every 8 hours to receive rich rewards, and click Christmas messenger to purchase or open gift boxes!\\n\\nActivity 3: Christmas Carnival in the Mining Area\\nActivity Description: In the mining area, all the monsters are carefully dressed up to play with players! The pits are filled with piles of gift boxes now. Go with your friends to get Christmas gifts!\\n\\nFor more follow-up activities and the latest news, please pay attention to in-game announcements in  [Sky Block], Google Play and Blockman Go platform.\\n\\n 【Sky Block】 Operation Group \\n\\nDecember 10, 2019
Item_Name570002=Thank you for your interest in and support for Sky Block. \\n\\n [Notice of Opening Service] \\nThe official IOS service and the official Android service are not sharing the same game data for the time being. The "Gcubes" obtained by players in any form will only be viewed and used by the same system platform. \\n [Prohibited Behaviors] \\n1. All account sharing, account transactions, illegal recharges, and etc. are prohibited. Beware of being deceived. \\n2. It is forbidden to use technical means to analyze, modify, attack and derive the game client. \\n3. It is forbidden to use plug-ins, third-party tools, and any improper means to undermine the fairness of the game. \\n [Customer Feedback] \\nData abnormalities, program bugs, device incompatibility, and recharge related abnormalities may occur during the game. Feel free to provide feedback in the following ways: \\n\\n Customer Service Email: bm_skyblock@outlook.com\\n\\n 【Sky Block】Operation Group \\n \\nDecember 10, 2019
Item_Name570003=Thank you for your interest in and support for Sky Block. In order to maintain a green and fair game environment and guarantee the interests of all players, we remind all players: \\n\\n1. It is forbidden to use plug-ins, third-party tools, and any improper means to undermine the fairness of the game. Based on system monitoring and player reports, if the above behaviors are found, we will regularly take actions such as deducting illegal revenue, freezing and banning game accounts. \\n\\n2. In order to protect the interests of players, please do not purchase accounts and recharge for others. Always beware of being deceived. If the account cannot be retrieved after being stolen due to the above situation, the officials will not handle it. \\n\\nTo create a good game environment, we need the efforts of all players. To this end, please supervise each other. If you find any illegal prohibited behaviors, please go for official customer service for report. Reward for the report will be given after reviewing and verifying the information. \\n\\nCustomer Service Email: bm_skyblock@outlook.com\\n\\n 【Sky Block】Operation Group \\n\\nDecember 10, 2019

