Item_Name570004=Thanks for your interest in and support of [Sky Block]. \\n[Sky Block] is planned to be continuously line updated on January 2nd, 2020. We will adjust and optimize the following parts of the game.\\n\\n[Mining Area Gift Box] When the gift box is destroyed, it will drop extra ore.\\n[Seven-day sign-in event] The rewards from the 3rd day to the 6th day are changed to some limited out of print Christmas theme blocks in the gift box.\\n[In-game UI adjustment] Party opening notifications have been moved to the top of the screen.\\n\\nWe apologize for any inconvenience and hesitation this adjustment has brought to players.\\n\\nThis adjustment has possibility to delay. Please follow the [Sky Block] in-game announcement, Google Play and Blockman-go platform to get the specific release time, as well as more follow-up and latest news.\\n\\n[Sky Block] Operations Group\\n\\nJanuary 2nd, 2020
Item_Name570005=Thank you for your attention and support for Sky Block.\\n[Update on Easter]\\nIn order to meet the needs of players and to welcome the Easter, we decided to organise a fountain discount eventEvent\\ntime: 2020.4.3-2020.4.12[Fountain discount]\\nFlickering Series [-20%]\\nGlittering Series [-50%]\\nShining Series [-50%]\\nFor more follow-up activities and latest news, please follow [Sky Block] in-game announcement, Google and Blockman Go game platform.
